testcase.title: verify xls format is accepted in exportRegulatoryResults request

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API
I pass a "format = xls and query = cancer and offset = 0 and hits = 20 and expectedValues = exportRegulatoryResults_Smoke_1.xls" as parameter to "exportRegulatoryResultsV2" operation
check the requested file is found in the following path "exportRegulatoryResults_Smoke_1.xls"
check for all the columns "Abstract,Comments,Coming into Force Date,Ready to Use Forms" in the file
